- [ ] Each voice sounds distinct?
- [ ] Voices not bleeding into each other?
- [ ] Post-liability-analysis responses show genuine change?
- [ ] Tensions enriched, not resolved?
- [ ] After Barnes analysis, options menu includes M/M response options?
- [ ] Scholar-on-Scholar explanation divergence treated as expected (cross-civilizational misperception), not violation?
- [ ] Variety: did each MIND use more than the single most obvious move (see MIND Variety above)?

